{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "亚斯拉姆（Fes限定Ver.） 第2话 为王，为父",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "旧王都 索尔·阿尔贝里亚",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "王都……没想到我还有\\n再回到这里的一天。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "毕竟至今为止都处于魔神的\\n掌控之下，没办法轻举妄动……\\n不过现在应该可以稍微放肆一点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "因为据说现在的狄涅尔皇帝\\n是那位艾缪尔少爷呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "艾缪尔吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "我所了解的这个世界的艾缪尔少爷，\\n是个没什么出众才华的孩子……\\n你那边的呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "怎么说呢……\\n他的确不像他的哥哥们那样，\\n有什么显而易见的才能……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "那么，这座城市之所以如此萧条，\\n看来并不是因为世界的差异呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "虽然一路走来已有所耳闻……\\n但还真是惨不忍睹。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "街道上几乎没什么人呢。\\n这副样子，\\n和亡国也没什么差别了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "也难怪会这样。\\n听说要是被新皇帝陛下盯上，\\n不知道会有怎样的刁难呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "好像有很多人表示\\n前任皇帝在位的时候\\n情况还比现在好一点呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "我本来还担心这里\\n脱离了魔神的掌控后\\n不知会变成什么样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "却没想到民众竟会怀念\\n魔神的支配。这也是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "“这也是我造的孽”吗？\\n你这句话我都听腻了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "不过，你和亚罗拉斯\\n都没有育儿的天赋\\n倒是千真万确的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "这我无法反驳……\\n但正因为如此，\\n我才要负起责任。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "负责？你要做什么……嗯？\\n那是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "很好，这里，就是这里！\\n要在这里建一座我的铜像！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "而且要是那种从街上\\n全方位可见的巨大铜像！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "巨大铜像……吗？\\n可是，这点地方根本不够\\n建那么大的东西啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "面积不够！？那把这一带\\n都夷为平地不就好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "您是说把这一带的房屋\\n都拆掉吗！？\\n那民众要怎么生活……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "啊！？你不知道平民的房子\\n和我的铜像哪个更重要吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "可、可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "艾缪尔那家伙……\\n知道自己在说什么吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "你冷静一点，亚斯拉姆。\\n就算你现在挺身而出，\\n也只会让事态变得更糟而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "我知道。因为现在的我\\n只是一个过客……要是能有一个\\n记得我样貌的人就好了……嗯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "艾缪尔殿下……哦不，陛下。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "嗯？是马格努斯啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "陛下，这件事\\n能交给我来办吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "交给你？好吧……\\n你可不要让我失望啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "结果一定会如陛下所愿。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "马格努斯大人……这样好吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "这可是谕旨。我们只能服从。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "那不是……马格努斯吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "马格努斯？听起来有点耳熟……\\n啊，没记错的话，是给艾缪尔少爷\\n当老师的那个骑士吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "他为人正直，最重要的是从不\\n阿谀奉承。我当初任命他也是觉得\\n他不会对王子有不必要的顾虑……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "他竟会听从那种命令，\\n真是难以置信……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "我果然……\\n还是不能袖手旁观……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "又有的忙了……\\n但是，现在要做的是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "马格努斯，我可不是为了\\n让你给艾缪尔擦屁股\\n才任命你当他的老师的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "什么？你是谁？\\n你若敢对殿下口出狂言，\\n我决不会放过你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "你不记得这张脸了吗，\\n马格努斯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "嗯！？难、难道是……\\n不，怎么可能……有这种事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "已经去世的人\\n以几十年前的相貌现身……\\n的确是挺荒唐的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "宫、宫廷魔法师大人也在！？\\n而且也是当年的容貌……\\n我这是在做梦吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "你也可以这么想。\\n就当是你的故主从死后的世界\\n回来给你忠告了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "来给我忠告……也对……\\n亚罗拉斯陛下不会\\n对王都的现状坐视不管。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "看来你也是明白人。\\n那么你为什么\\n不采取行动呢，马格努斯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "你是一个清高之士，对不正当行为的\\n厌恶程度比我更甚。我还记得\\n你常顶撞我说弄虚作假不可饶恕。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "的确有过这样的事呢……\\n真是惭愧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "你不需要感到惭愧。\\n正因为你是这样的人，\\n我才放心地把艾缪尔交给了你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "当年的你一定比任何人\\n都无法忍受王都的这副惨状。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "你为什么要纵容艾缪尔呢？\\n你要谏言斥责他的暴行，有必要的话\\n甚至不惜讨伐他才是你的职责所在。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "回答陛下啊，马格努斯。\\n王亲自向你提问，\\n你无权保持沉默。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "我仿佛……回到了几十年前。\\n回想起来，昔日的宫廷魔法师大人\\n也是如此劝谏我的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "毕竟你的性格比亚罗拉斯还乖僻。\\n我身为宫廷魔法师\\n也忍不住要抱怨几句。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "是啊……真让人怀念。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "嗯。不过，我不是来和你叙旧的。\\n回答我的问题，马格努斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "因为我相信艾缪尔大人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "相信……你信他什么？\\n艾缪尔的哪一点\\n值得你如此信任呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "我相信他的“才能”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "才能？艾缪尔少爷吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "我懂您的意思。\\n艾缪尔大人在王室子嗣中\\n确实是最不像陛下的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "你是想说他缺乏作为\\n统治者的才能对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "也可以这样认为……\\n但艾缪尔大人自己比任何人\\n都有自知之明。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "艾缪尔大人非常清楚\\n“靠自己是什么都做不到的”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "我认为这是被称为“贤王”的\\n亚罗拉斯陛下也不具备的\\n身为统治者的才能。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "我知道你很看好艾缪尔的才能\\n并对他的未来抱有期待了。\\n但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "民众现在正因为\\n艾缪尔的暴政而备受煎熬。\\n如果对此坐视不管，还谈什么统治。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "我知道。但我认为艾缪尔大人\\n萌生身为王者的自觉之前，\\n只要由我们来辅佐他就好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "你那份忠心虽然可贵……\\n但连身为王者的自觉都没有\\n就登上王座才是最根本的错误吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "既然已经自称为王，\\n艾缪尔就要承担起责任。\\n那是他需要亲自担起的责任。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "如果不能担起这份责任，\\n那他就没有资格当王。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "您说得对。这的确是我所敬爱的\\n亚罗拉斯陛下会说的话。但是……\\n您可曾站在艾缪尔大人的立场上想过？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "艾缪尔大人比他人\\n更想改变当下的状况。\\n他一直备受煎熬，渴望得到帮助。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "既然如此，支持并帮助他\\n才是作为父亲应该做的吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "我可不记得命令过你\\n当他的父亲……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "是的，我并不想僭越。\\n但若父亲本人不行动，\\n就只能由我代劳了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0081",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0082",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "恕我冒昧，如今的艾缪尔大人\\n需要的是陛下您。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0083",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "您说得对。\\n昏君、暴君的确该废黜。\\n这是身为明君应有的决断。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0084",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120208_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马格努斯",
            "context": "但是，作为一位父亲，\\n我并不认为试图舍弃\\n孩子的未来这一决断是对的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0085",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110334_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "亚斯拉姆",
            "context": "作为父亲吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110334_02_01_0086",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}